    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five operating points. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated context of use.",
